<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Hammer Talisman</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Hammer Talisman" src="/file/Elden-Ring/hammer_talisman_talisman_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="hammer talisman talisman elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Weight</td> 
     <td>0.9</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <img src="/file/Elden-Ring/status_effect_99_elden_ring_wiki_guide_44px.png" alt="status effect 99 elden ring wiki guide 44px" width="21" height="21">&nbsp;Increases&nbsp; 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stamina" href="/Stamina" target="">Stamina</a>&nbsp;damage against blocking enemies by 40% 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Hammer Talisman</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Talismans" href="/Talismans">Talisman</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>.&nbsp;Hammer Talisman&nbsp;increases <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stamina" href="/Stamina" target="">Stamina</a> damage against blocking enemies by 20%. Players can use talismans&nbsp;in Elden Ring to boost a variety of&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stats" href="/Stats" target="">Stats</a>. Updated to <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A talisman depicting a hammer and a knight.<br>Enhances stamina-reducing attacks against a blocking opponent.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Hammers are highly effective against shield-bearing foes, so much so that they are known as "knight-killers."</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Hammer Talisman Effect</h3> 
<p>Hammer Talisman&nbsp;increases&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stamina" href="/Stamina" target="">Stamina</a>&nbsp;damage against blocking enemies by 40%.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Hammer Talisman</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Recusant Henricus" href="/Recusant+Henricus">Recusant Henricus</a>, located north of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Warmaster's Shack" href="/Warmaster's+Shack">Warmaster's Shack</a>, and northeast of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stormhill Shack" href="/Stormhill+Shack" target="">Stormhill Shack</a>. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=526&amp;lat=-172.960937&amp;lng=100.262171&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=526&amp;lat=-172.960937&amp;lng=100.262171&amp;zoom=8">Map link</a>]</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Hammer Talisman Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Sell value:&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="runes currency elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;500</li> 
 <li>Has no effect on general stance-breaking;&nbsp;only works against shield blocks.</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff6600;">Note:</span> This Weapon was changed in&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>&nbsp;as follows: Stamina Buff has been increased from 20% to 40%.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
